### 9. COIN ADMIN
### ════════════════════════════════════════════

### 9.1 Set/Update Config
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/wallet/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "minEligibleAmount": 100,
  "maxEligibleAmount": 1000,
  "rewardPercentMin": 5,
  "rewardPercentMax": 8,
  "maxCoinsPerOrder": 50,
  "redeemPercentLimit": 10,
  "returnPeriodDays": 7
}

### 9.2 Get Config
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/wallet/config
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9.3 Get Analytics
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/wallet/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9.4 Manual Trigger Activation
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/wallet/trigger-activation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


